                Privacy Policy Transcom Foods Limited is committed to protecting the privacy of personal information you may provide Us on this Website (the Site). We believe it is important for you to know how We treat your personal information. The terms of this Privacy Policy apply to all users of this Site. If you do not agree with the terms of this Privacy Policy, you should immediately cease the use of this Site.</p>
